wiki.summary: "Intro" is Khalid’s introduction to the 2019 album "Free Spirit". Khalid describes a relationship that he is clinging to, despite the fact that it is clearly not working out, because he doesn’t know who he is outside of it and is terrified of facing the world outside of the safe, secure context of a relationship. wiki.content: "Intro" is Khalid’s introduction to the 2019 album "Free Spirit". Khalid describes a relationship that he is clinging to, despite the fact that it is clearly not working out, because he doesn’t know who he is outside of it and is terrified of facing the world outside of the safe, secure context of a relationship. "I wanted people to find their own name for this song and what it means to them. It was made to be the intro: I’m naming it ‘Intro.’ No other name popped up in my head. It’s so cinematic and it washes over you, and I’m like, ‘People have to hear this first.'” - Khalid for Apple Music Read more on Last.fm.
